data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN @ 2.25% - an amazing opportunity to buy today at an interest rate from days gone by. This updated beauty is located on a quiet cul-de-sac. Barn doors open to the den/office (possible 5th bedroom) overlooking the front porch. Beautiful wood laminate floors downstairs, crown molding, custom tile, & 10' ceilings are many of the custom features of this home. Kitchen includes a large island w/dining bar, pantry closet, double ovens, gas cooktop, eating area, custom tile floors, & access to the backyard. Downstairs bedroom & full bath. Upstairs loft. Spacious primary suite w/walk-in closet including custom built ins. Primary suite bath has double sinks, soaking tub and separate shower. Solar heated swimming pool w/waterfall. Located close to schools, park, & shopping. Solar w/low monthly payment lowering your monthly utility cost! No HOA and no Mello-Roos!
